snippet.textDisplay:
When I was growing up "Lutti Heer ve Fakir Di" used to be my favourite track from Hans Raj Hans...This is the song that has become my body organ as it was constantly heard by me and I always found that HRH songs those days carried a sense of sufisim even though they were embedded in more commercial and pop based tracks. 
Mr Hitesh Sonik and MTV
great going guys...the people you are bringing on to the TV are our ambassadors of culture and music. We need to cherish their presence in our culture.
